l pathways in adolescents compared with adults. Dobberfuhl AD, Oti T, Sakamoto H, and Marson L. Identification of \{CNS\} neurons innervating the levator ani and ventral bulbospongiosus muscles in male rats. J Sex Med 2014;11:664–677. "
